00:27:01.550 --> 00:27:03.530 align:middle line:90%
And that's why our side won.

00:27:03.530 --> 00:27:05.420 align:middle line:90%
Now we produce 8%.

00:27:05.420 --> 00:27:08.600 align:middle line:84%
And most of the rest is
produced by countries

00:27:08.600 --> 00:27:10.430 align:middle line:90%
