we break their power.

00:27:18.410 --> 00:27:20.430 align:middle line:84%
It's oil money that's
funding the jihadis.

00:27:20.430 --> 00:27:21.074 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Mhm.

00:27:21.074 --> 00:27:22.240 align:middle line:90%
>>ZUBRIN: It's oil funding--

00:27:22.240 --> 00:27:23.490 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's exactly right.

00:27:23.490 --> 00:27:25.565 align:middle line:90%
They funded the 9/11 terrorists.

00:27:25.565 --> 00:27:26.360 align:middle line:90%
>>ZUBRIN: Right.

00:27:26.360 --> 00:27:28.930 align:middle line:10%
I mean, it's Saudi money
that funds the Taliban that

00:27:28.930 --> 00:27:31.750 align:middle line:10%
