national security.

00:27:40.410 --> 00:27:41.993 align:middle line:84%
It's the most important
thing we could

00:27:41.993 --> 00:27:44.430 align:middle line:84%
do to make sure that
the world of the future

00:27:44.430 --> 00:27:46.992 align:middle line:84%
